---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — inpro" description="What inpro is, who runs it, and how content is verified.">
  <article class="about">
    <h1>About inpro</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      inpro is an unofficial, community-maintained PCS info portal for Wiesbaden, Germany.
      It exists because new arrivals waste days chasing answers spread across a dozen sources.
    </p>

    <h2>Not affiliated</h2>
    <p>
      inpro is not run by, endorsed by, or affiliated with the US Army, the Department of Defense, or USAG Wiesbaden.
      All content is public, unclassified, and compiled from official sources and community knowledge.
      For official policy, always confirm with your unit S1 or the relevant garrison office.
    </p>

    <h2>How content is verified</h2>
    <p>
      Every page cites its sources in tiers:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>T1 — Official</strong>: Army, DoD, TRICARE, DoDEA, USAG, MyArmyBenefits.</li>
      <li><strong>T2 — Semi-official</strong>: MilitaryOneSource, AFN, Stars &amp; Stripes, Army G1.</li>
      <li><strong>T3 — Community</strong>: Expat blogs, Reddit, public-facing FB pages. Paraphrased, never quoted.</li>
      <li><strong>T4 — German-side</strong>: Stadt Wiesbaden, ADAC, Bürgeramt.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>
      Every page shows a "Last verified" date. Entries older than 60 days get flagged automatically for re-verification.
      POCs marked "Verify before acting" change frequently — always call ahead.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      No tracking cookies. No accounts. The profile you set for filtering lives only in your browser's local storage — we never see it.
      Aggregate pageview counts are collected via Cloudflare Web Analytics, with no cookies and no personal data.
    </p>

    <h2>Found something wrong?</h2>
    <p>
      Use the "Report outdated info" link at the bottom of any page. Corrections are welcome and fast.
    </p>
  </article>

  <style>
    .about { max-width: 44rem; }
    .about .lead { font-family: var(--font-sans); font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--muted); }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
